name: jim taylor (jiMTV)
text: Pastor Paul presides over an open and affirming house of worship.  My experience has been that nobody thinks they have it all figured out and nobody tries to lay their trip on you. Bring love and you will find love here.  Open communion on first and third Sundays.

name: valarie mcclellan
text: Great Church service. Easy location. Great congregation.

name: Tom Barr
text: Excellent church and venue.  Open to all, loving members and Christ oriented church.

name: John Moseley
text: Covenant Community Church and Pilgrim Church share this facility.  Two congratulations worshipping at different times works very well.
